255
00:23:43,755 --> 00:23:45,173
<i>Kuperingatkan kau.</i>

256
00:23:45,256 --> 00:23:47,342
Jangan mengikutiku lagi.

257
00:23:50,428 --> 00:23:51,513
Jang Han-na.

258
00:23:51,805 --> 00:23:53,014
<i>Mengerti?</i>

259
