aku harus belajar darinya.

293
00:27:14,507 --> 00:27:16,009
<i>Kembali?</i>

294
00:27:16,718 --> 00:27:20,847
<i>Tunggu sebentar.</i>
<i>Apa Kang Cheong-ya keluar asrama?</i>

295
00:28:01,012 --> 00:28:04,182
Pengisi dayanya pasti ada di sekitar sini.

296
