00:35:17,323 --> 00:35:18,908
Tunggu apa lagi? Masuk! Cepat!

353
00:35:32,297 --> 00:35:34,883
<i>Itu sebabnya aku</i>
<i>menyuruhmu menangkap Han-na!</i>

354
00:35:35,049 --> 00:35:39,220
