00:36:59,384 --> 00:37:00,885
Putri direktur ANSP?

362
00:37:07,725 --> 00:37:09,602
Apa maksudnya?

363
00:37:10,520 --> 00:37:13,314
"Mereka tak akan membiarkan
putri direktur ANSP mati"?

364
00:37:17,026 --> 00:37:18,820
Bukan apa-apa.

365
00:37:20,446 --> 00:37:22,073
Wanita sial.

366
00:37:23,158 --> 00:37:24,033
Hei.

367
00:37:24,659 --> 00:37:26,578
Kau masih meremehkanku?

368
00:37:28,163 --> 00:37:30,623
Tak ada komunis
yang akan menyelamatkanmu di sini.

369
00:37:33,751 --> 00:37:35,837
Bicaralah selagi aku bertanya baik-baik.

370
00:37:36,171 --> 00:37:37,338
Cepat.

371
00:37:41,509 --> 00:37:42,635
Sebenarnya...

372
00:37:59,235 --> 00:38:00,528
Ya ampun,

373
00:38:00,612 --> 00:38:02,447
lagunya sangat bagus.

374
00:38:02,655 --> 00:38:04,240
Suci sekali.

375
00:38:10,872 --> 00:38:11,998
Pak.

376
00:38:13,208 --> 00:38:14,584
Bangun, Pak!

377
00:38:15,585 --> 00:38:18,129
Putri direktur ANSP ada di sini.

378
00:38:19,005 --> 00:38:22,550
Kenapa tak kau manfaatkan
kesempatan hebat itu?

379
00:38:24,511 --> 00:38:27,055
Apa maksudmu?

380
00:38:27,138 --> 00:38:29,891
Putri direktur ANSP ada di sini?

381
00:38:37,315 --> 00:38:38,441
