Benar, bukan?

417
00:40:48,404 --> 00:40:50,615
Kau membelanya karena kau mata-mata ANSP?

418
00:40:51,741 --> 00:40:53,159
Eun Yeong-ro.

419
00:40:54,744 --> 00:40:56,496
Dengar baik-baik.

420
00:40:58,498 --> 00:41:00,708
Dahulu, berat kakakku 78 kg,

421
00:41:00,959 --> 00:41:03,586
tapi setelah sebulan dikurung di ANSP,

422
